Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:47.27,OP CN,,0,0,0,,帶著絕對的信念 故事就此展開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:53.32,OP CN,,0,0,0,,Tell Me 活下去就是「堅強」的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:01:01.33,OP CN,,0,0,0,,用孤獨描繪的Perfect Style 奮力破壞了它 得到了它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:04.33,OP CN,,0,0,0,,所有的回音都重疊在One Place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:12.96,OP CN,,0,0,0,,無論何時(Believe) 你都在身邊(You're always there for me)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.14,OP CN,,0,0,0,,讓我看到真正的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:25.73,OP CN,,0,0,0,,BREAK OUT! BREAK OUT! Just do it now 毫不動搖的羈絆以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:32.27,OP CN,,0,0,0,,Non-Stop BREAK OUT! BREAK OUT! Believe in my soul 更火熱一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:35.65,OP CN,,0,0,0,,懷抱不下 (So they will never know)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:38.91,OP CN,,0,0,0,,漸行漸遠的夢想(That's all right)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:41.62,OP CN,,0,0,0,,BREAK OUT! BREAK OUT! 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:26.30,OP CN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:34.83,ED CN,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it? 相遇瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:41.79,ED CN,,0,0,0,,我內心一悸 已墜入愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:47.63,ED CN,,0,0,0,,若誠實相告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:51.22,ED CN,,0,0,0,,定會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:55.68,ED CN,,0,0,0,,受你嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,生平初次的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:10.91,ED CN,,0,0,0,,但凡在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:20.42,ED CN,,0,0,0,,不覺間 笑容便會浮上唇角
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:28.38,ED CN,,0,0,0,,You don't let me down. 明明該是滿溢的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:36.27,ED CN,,0,0,0,,但凡分隔兩地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:45.65,ED CN,,0,0,0,,不覺間 胸口就滿是不安
